  ('3693', 'INDUSTRIAL ASSEMBLY MACHINES', '1979-05-15', null, 'Industrial Assembly Machines', 'Industrial Production Type Power Screwdriving Machines; Circuit Card Assembly Machines.', 'Specialized Ammunition and Ordnance Assembly Machines; Wrapping and Packaging Machinery; Metalworking Machinery; Hand Tools.', 'This class includes equipment specifically designed to assemble pre-fabricated components without further design machining of the components. Equipment designed to perform combined machining and assembling operations which result in material removal are classified in classes other than this class. Also excluded are items for which more specific classifications are suitable', '36 - SPECIAL INDUSTRY MACHINERY', null, '5.0', 'Industrial Products & Services', '5.1', 'Machinery & Components'),
