  ('81', 'CONTAINERS/PACKAGING/PACKING SUPPL', '1979-10-01', null, null, null, null, 'A chest, case, box, roll, bag, or other container, when specifically designed for housing of a set, kit, outfit, or individual item (with or without attachments or spares), for its protection when not in use, or for the convenience of the user, is classified in the same class as the item or items for which designed, or in such other class as is appropriate. However, when the chest, case, box, roll, bag, or other container is primarily a shipping container, it is classified in group 81.', null, null, null, null, null, null),
