  ('9630', 'ADDITIVE METAL MATERIALS', '1979-02-15', null, 'Additive Metal Materials', 'Alloying additives (Aluminum, Antimony, Copper, and Others).', 'Fuel Inhibiting Additives (FSC 6850).', 'Only bulk material will be identified in this class. Additive metal materials are those which are added to metals to improve their characteristics as required (e.g., lead added to steel to improve the machinability).', '96 - ORES, MINERALS AND PRIMARY PRODUCTS', null, '5.0', 'Industrial Products & Services', '5.6', 'Basic Materials'),
